def: Of or pertaining to internodes; intervening between nodes orjoints.
Having the quality of excreting, or throwing offexcrementitious matter.
So as to torture. Beau. & Fl.
To affect at heart; to shock. [R.] "The seek to heartstrikeus." B. Jonson.
A tribe of Indians who formerly inhabited Eastern Connecticut.[Written also Pequods.]
Drawn outside of; -- used to designate a circle that touchesone of the sides of a given triangle, and also the other two sidesproduced.
One skilled in strategy, or the science of directing greatmilitary movements.
A genus of beautiful South American passerine birds, includingthe cock of the rock.
A prefix used adjectively and adverbially in the sense ofamiss, wrong, ill, wrongly, unsuitably; as, misdeed, mislead,mischief, miscreant.
